            Workflows["🔵 Workflows\n**Orchestration**\nPipeline Flow"]
            Logging["🟩 Cloud Logging\n**Logs · Metrics**\nHealth Check"]
        end

    end

    %% ===== PRIMARY FLOWS (solid lines) =====
    User       -->|HTTPS|                       Frontend
    Frontend   -->|API Call / HTTPS|            BackendAPI
